OPTIVISION TECHN said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 42.80% to NT$61,127,000 from NT$106,858,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2011           5/2010
Sales             61,127          106,858    
YOY%             -42.80%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            361,294          461,944    
YOY%             -21.79% 
=================================================================
 